{"type":"message","id":"8f194994","parentId":"d9782f38","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:45:15.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"@tencent-weixin 目录是空的！这就是问题所在。微信插件（openclaw-weixin）指向的路径 `~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@tencent-weixin/` 是空的，没有任何文件。\n\n安装微信插件时，它被链接到这个位置，但实际上这个目录是空的。当 OpenClaw 加载这个插件时失败，导致整个通信中断。\n\n现在让我看看安装的当前状态和是否有其他相关问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"c23115e2fae5feb81aaf203f26d0261b7247a7f876132978c1b12bc9152cd8f2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mvdjqfqee3s3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-weixin && pwd && ls -la"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mvdjqfqee3s3_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"file ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-weixin"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":200,"output":155,"cacheRead":33088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778377506084,"responseId":"064f1622ccc7b1b81bc7cfb0b4dd2681"}}
