{"type":"message","id":"3e9c4465","parentId":"25588446","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:45:36.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The symbolic link is broken! The openclaw-weixin extension points to a path that doesn't exist. The `@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin` directory is empty.\n\nLet me check if there's a weixin plugin that's installed elsewhere, and also understand the issue. When you install the weixin plugin, it's supposed to create a symbolic link in extensions/. But the target doesn't exist.\n\nLet me also check if the WeChat plugin was previously installed and what happened. Looking at the log earlier, I saw:\n```\n[gateway] [plugins] installed plugin package requires compiled runtime output for TypeScript entry index.ts: expected ./dist/index.js, ./dist/index.mjs, ./dist/index.cjs, index.js, index.mjs, index.cjs (plugin=openclaw-weixin, source=/home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/.openclaw-install-stage-KKwmxb)\n\n\n```\n\nThis error from the May 5th log shows that openclaw-weixin was being installed but had a TypeScript entry problem - it didn't have the expected compiled output files. Now I need to check what's currently in the extensions directory to understand the full picture.\n\nLooking at the directory listing, openclaw-weixin is a broken symbolic link pointing to an empty directory. When the user tries to install the WeChat plugin, it's breaking the entire communication system, likely because the broken link is causing issues across the plugin loading process.\n\nI should help them either remove the broken symbolic link or reinstall the plugin properly to fix the communication failure.\n\n```\n","thinkingSignature":"de984e4e10f89bc53080ced6f73fb2fd1c164017016263a882c368ec7c87a8b6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到问题了。**`openclaw-weixin` 是一个坏掉的符号链接**：\n\n```\nopenclaw-weixin → /home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin （空目录）\n```\n\n这就是装微信插件后整个通信挂掉的原因——坏链接影响了整个插件系统的加载。\n\n**两个方案：**\n\n**方案 A：删掉坏链接，临时恢复**\n```bash\nrm ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-weixin\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n之后飞书恢复正常，但微信插件还是没装上。\n\n**方案 B：重装微信插件（修复链接）**\n需要先找到正确的安装方式——之前安装失败是因为插件包没有编译输出（TypeScript 直接分发，没有 `dist/index.js`）。\n\n你之前是怎么安装的？是 `npm install` 还是从某个市场装的？先搞清楚来源，我帮你找正确的安装方式。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":171,"output":495,"cacheRead":33280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778377515746,"responseId":"064f162cf3c9811f098f07076c7a4d4d"}}
