{"type":"message","id":"075f1485","parentId":"e7ca9101","timestamp":"2026-05-10T02:13:16.652Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is referring to the interactive card from TK 选品大师 that was showing \"app secret invalid\" errors. They mention they just granted edit permissions in the selection doc (多维表). \n\nThe issue isn't about permissions on the doc - the error is about the app credentials (App Secret) being invalid for the tts Feishu bot account. The tts bot's App Secret has expired or been rotated, and the saved credentials in the config no longer match what's on the Feishu Open Platform.\n\nThe user needs to go to https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a930f78f51399bc6 and get a fresh App Secret, then update the config.\n\n\nI should ask them to verify whether the App Secret has actually been updated on the Feishu side, and if so, I'll need to refresh the credentials in the configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"48de5d8a9653217c3a14921c195aa672ab9a937f3fc14e05c4fbecf268d827c0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这个错误是 **tts 机器人的 App Secret 失效**，不是多维表权限问题。\n\n去飞书开放平台重新获取 Secret：\n👉 [https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a930f78f51399bc6](https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a930f78f51399bc6)\n\n**凭证与基础信息** → **App Secret** → 重置/查看\n\n拿到新 Secret 之后发给我，我帮你更新到配置里。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11400,"output":280,"cacheRead":34816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778379184558,"responseId":"064f1cb026ae95b7d40c42dad3a9014f"}}
