{"type":"message","id":"0062ebc6","parentId":"c3ae4370","timestamp":"2026-05-10T09:45:26.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is from the agent-orchestrator bot conversation (it's a different chat - the user is talking to the agent-orchestrator bot directly on Feishu). The issue is that the Agent 编排工程师 bot doesn't have permissions to access Feishu docs and Bitable (多维表格).\n\nThis is a Feishu app permissions issue, not an OpenClaw configuration issue. The bot needs to be granted the proper permissions in the Feishu developer console.\n\nLet me check - the user is now talking to me (kiit/main agent) and forwarding the message from agent-orchestrator's conversation. The agent-orchestrator bot is a separate Feishu app (cli_a9558a1795799bb5) and it needs to be configured with the right permissions in Feishu's developer console.\n\n\nI need to walk the user through adding the necessary document and Bitable permissions to the Agent 编排工程师 app in the Feishu developer console.","thinkingSignature":"07241b88cd3b251ba984589c6983e01db66f462b3c73de67174b33e4325aba70"},{"type":"text","text":"这是**飞书应用权限**的问题，不是 OpenClaw 配置问题。\n\n`agent-orchestrator` 是独立的应用（`cli_a9558a1795799bb5`），需要在飞书开放平台给它开通文档和多维表格权限：\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 打开 → [https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a9558a1795799bb5](https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a9558a1795799bb5)\n2. 进入 **「权限管理」**\n3. 搜索并开通以下权限：\n   - `docx:document:readonly` （云文档 读）\n   - `docx:document:write` （云文档 写）\n   - `bitable:app:readonly` （多维表格 读）\n   - `bitable:app:write` （多维表格 写）\n4. 点击 **「申请发版」** 或 **「直接发布」**\n\n开通后我这边重启一下 Gateway 让权限生效。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":169,"output":412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":45629,"totalTokens":46210,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778406312575,"responseId":"064f86a90036b32c5d94c34c68498894"}}
