{"type":"message","id":"3d52c913","parentId":"84633702","timestamp":"2026-05-10T10:57:09.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the logs, the agent-orchestrator is running and processing (I can see sessions with `agent:agent-orchestrator`). But I don't see specific permission errors for feishu doc/bitable access.\n\nThe error message from the agent says \"没有权限\" - this could mean:\n1. The feishu app doesn't have the API permissions published/deployed\n2. The specific document/bitable doesn't have the bot added as a collaborator\n\nAlso critically - I notice the binding for `agent-orchestrator` was NOT added successfully earlier (the edit failed). Let me verify the bindings are in the config.\n","thinkingSignature":"feeff3fe46ee80033c051561f0f20d44ef4156736cb004fcf850c41b15764754"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n日志看，agent-orchestrator 在线且在跑。但我没看到飞书文档权限的具体报错。\n\n两件事需要确认：\n\n**1. binding 可能没写入成功**（之前编辑报错了）\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4rcrj625khk5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A5 \"bindings\" ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20135,"output":208,"cacheRead":51392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71735,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778410617740,"responseId":"064f977a28f3e72a564757cfae7f112d"}}
