{"type":"message","id":"902c0ff8","parentId":"40acd4d6","timestamp":"2026-05-10T10:57:33.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - the bindings are correctly configured for agent-orchestrator. No permission errors in the logs either. \n\nThe issue is more likely that:\n1. The feishu app's token cache doesn't have the new permissions yet\n2. Or the Gateway needs a restart to pick up the new permissions (the earlier restart was for app secret, but maybe the token cache needs to be refreshed)\n\nLet me check if the agent-orchestrator feishu connection is working by looking at the recent log entries for that specific channel/account.\n","thinkingSignature":"8023e09b6e9e68a0e471841d1f24288e39f2c852183c39e02c5e9af7d500d8b0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dq259vrmqnab_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -300 /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-05-10.log 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"agent-orchestrator.*start\\|agent-orchestrator.*error\\|agent-orchestrator.*ws\\|feishu.*agent-orch\" | tail -15"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":295,"output":191,"cacheRead":71488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71974,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778410639263,"responseId":"064f978ffcf1481ac0fa26aeb9d4ee3a"}}
