{"type":"message","id":"92f064a3","parentId":"fee03afd","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:02:53.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So there are several feishu-related skills in plugin-skills:- feishu-doc- feishu-drive\n- feishu-perm\n- feishu-wiki\n\nThese are in `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/`. The error mentioned `feishu-create-doc` which doesn't exist. But `feishu-doc` does exist.\n\nThe user is asking if there's a global skill. The plugin-skills are available globally. The issue is that the error says `feishu-create-doc` doesn't exist, but `feishu-doc` does.\n\nLet me check if there's a way to look at what skills the agent-orchestrator is trying to use, or if `feishu-create-doc` is supposed to be an alias or something.\n\n\nThe agent is looking for `feishu-create-doc` but it's not installed—only `feishu-doc` is available. I should explain this mismatch to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"eeb3486fd4c838bfc46c8950dd07f1a0e50ac1b120e31d07912e8911fea72a9c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n`feishu-create-doc` 没有装。当前有的飞书 Skill 是：\n\n- `feishu-doc` （飞书文档读写）\n- `feishu-drive` （云盘管理）\n- `feishu-perm` （权限管理）\n- `feishu-wiki` （知识库）\n\n你说的报错是 `feishu-create-doc`——这个 Skill 不存在，但 `feishu-doc` 有创建文档的能力。\n\n**两个方案：**\n\n1. **直接用 `feishu-doc`**：它已经支持创建文档，Skill 配置正确就能用\n2. **或者你想装的 Skill 名字有误？** 告诉我具体想做什么，我来确认用哪个 Skill\n\n现在的问题是 Agent 找不到这个 Skill 文件，不影响飞书权限。你先确认下想让 Agent编排工程师 具体做什么操作？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":181,"output":367,"cacheRead":72320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72868,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778410957603,"responseId":"064f98cd891b5225813bf1fd8b694e79"}}
