{"type":"message","id":"3c279e6e","parentId":"a5356742","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:04:17.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about Feishu's CLI - they're confusing two different things:\n\n1. **Feishu Open Platform CLI (feishu CLI)** - This is a command-line tool for interacting with Feishu's open API. It has nothing to do with OpenClaw's skills.\n\n2. **OpenClaw skills** - These are the skill files (.md) that define how the AI agent uses tools.\n\nThe user seems to think that because Feishu's own CLI tools have certain capabilities (like creating docs, bitable operations, etc.), OpenClaw should automatically have access to those. But that's not how it works - OpenClaw needs specific skill files to interface with Feishu's APIs.\n\n\nI should clarify that these are separate systems: Feishu's platform capabilities aren't automatically available to OpenClaw just because they're part of Feishu's ecosystem - OpenClaw needs its own configured skills to access those same APIs.\n","thinkingSignature":"c9f8c39d53e29842bdbb2845de410679d20dd22f59709b004c4744946631a190"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你搞混了两个东西：\n\n**飞书开放平台的 CLI** → 是飞书官方工具，用来调用飞书 API，和 OpenClaw 无关。\n\n**OpenClaw Skill** → 是 AI Agent 调用工具的方式，每一个 Skill 就是一个 `.md` 配置文件，告诉 AI 怎么用飞书 API。\n\n飞书 CLI 有功能 ≠ OpenClaw 自动会用。OpenClaw 需要明确安装对应的 Skill 文件才能调用飞书 API。\n\n`agent-orchestrator` 报错是因为它去找 `feishu-create-doc` 这个 Skill，但这个 Skill 没装。**不是说飞书权限不够，是 Skill 缺失。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1004,"output":319,"cacheRead":71744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73067,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778411041669,"responseId":"064f992295c784f4a30420115608dd39"}}
