{"type":"message","id":"ad401d39","parentId":"bb16c3fb","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:05:23.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether I (KIIT, the main agent) also can't use feishu-doc because it's not installed globally. Let me check if feishu-doc is available to me.\n","thinkingSignature":"44d87c9187605a05e0fa41b82145fd9293aea100b5a69cb2efeb072dbd991fbe"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，我也没有。`feishu-doc` 这个 Skill 没有装到全局。\n\n目前已装的飞书 Skill 只有这些：\n- `feishu-doc`\n- `feishu-drive`\n- `feishu-perm`\n- `feishu-wiki`\n\n但实际上这些都是**空的**——没有对应的 Skill 实现文件。\n\n**所以现在的情况是：所有 Agent（kiit、tts、agent-orchestrator）都没有可用的飞书文档 Skill。** 要让我能用，需要先安装真正的飞书 Skill。\n\n用 `clawhub` 可以搜索和安装：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bo6uxd7da9a3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which clawhub 2>/dev/null || npx clawhub search feishu 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":486,"output":209,"cacheRead":72448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778411112498,"responseId":"064f99693e031bf891d7a008f44ca680"}}
