{"type":"message","id":"aae847e4","parentId":"a72a87c2","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:05:43.871Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a `create-feishu-doc` skill available on ClawHub. But actually, looking at what's already installed, `feishu-doc` skill in `plugin-skills/` should already support creating documents. Let me check what `feishu-doc` SKILL.md says about creation.\n","thinkingSignature":"b442f4b3450f33d881b3a986615033929cf2d4e43b56e06edb98182e9105f045"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_36co9wayp36k_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/plugin-skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":583,"output":115,"cacheRead":72896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778411131275,"responseId":"064f997ba4b9f83b5781690a991f6d35"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8c2f303","parentId":"aae847e4","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:05:43.916Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_36co9wayp36k_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations, including table creation for Docx.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\n\n[182 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778411143916}}
