{"type":"message","id":"514a66d1","parentId":"b781ef91","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:07:04.883Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gxdg1eno7xd3_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/.clawhub/lock.json:    \"create-feishu-doc\": {\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/.clawhub/origin.json:  \"slug\": \"create-feishu-doc\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:  \"name\": \"create-feishu-doc\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:  \"main\": \"scripts/create_feishu_doc.py\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:    \"test\": \"python scripts/create_feishu_doc.py\"\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:    \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/clawhub/create-feishu-doc\"\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:  \"homepage\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/create-feishu-doc\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/SKILL.md:name: create-feishu-doc\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/SKILL.md:description: \"Use this skill whenever the user wants to create, generate, write to, or organize content into a Feishu document. Triggers include: any mention of 'Feishu doc', 'Feishu document', '飞书文档', '创建飞书文档', '生成飞书文档', or requests to produce structured or complete documents within Feishu. This applies to scenarios requiring fully formatted documents, including but not limited to: technical documentation, PRDs, project plans, reports, notes, articles, or novels. Use this skill whenever content needs to be compiled, structured, and delivered as a Feishu document.\"\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/SKILL.md:本技能提供通用的飞书文档创建功能，根据用户提供的任意内容创建文档。支持各种文档类型：小说、技术文档、项目计划、报告、笔记、文章等。由于飞书文档API对单次写入内容长度有限制，本技能通过智能分段、分批写入和重试机制确保各种长文档的完整创建。\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/SKILL.md:1. create_doc(\"剑来小说第一章\")\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/SKILL.md:1. create_doc(\"Python编程指南\")\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/SKILL.md:### scripts/create_feishu_doc.py\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:# create-feishu-doc v1.0.4\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:1. **修改创建文档实现**：不再直接调用API，改为使用飞书文档工具创建\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:2. **优化等待机制**：创建文档成功后等待2秒才开始追加内容\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:- 使用飞书文档工具创建文档\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:from create_feishu_doc import FeishuDocCreator\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:# 创建文档创建器\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/README.md:# 完整流程：创建文档并填充内容"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6026,"aggregated":"/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/.clawhub/lock.json:    \"create-feishu-doc\": {\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/.clawhub/origin.json:  \"slug\": \"create-feishu-doc\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:  \"name\": \"create-feishu-doc\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:  \"main\": \"scripts/create_feishu_doc.py\",\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:    \"test\": \"python scripts/create_feishu_doc.py\"\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:    \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/clawhub/create-feishu-doc\"\n/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/skills/create-feishu-doc/package.json:  \"h