{"type":"message","id":"d5d238b7","parentId":"514a66d1","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:07:27.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the answer! Looking at the memory search results from `memory/2026-03-25-tiktok-shop.md`, there was a plugin called `openclaw-lark` that had a skill called `feishu-create-doc` for creating Feishu cloud documents. This was from March 2026.\n\nBut this was part of a separate plugin/package (`openclaw-lark`) that was apparently available before. The user is asking about which Agent previously created cloud documents - it was `openclaw-lark` plugin which contained `feishu-create-doc` skill.\n\nLooking at the current state:\n\n\n- `feishu-create-doc` skill doesn't exist in the current skill directories\n- `openclaw-lark` directory exists at `~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/` but only has `skills/tts-product-selection`\n- The user might be confusing `feishu-create-doc` (the skill from `openclaw-lark`) with `create-feishu-doc` (the new one I just installed from clawhub)\n- The old `openclaw-lark` plugin had `feishu-create-doc` as a skill that was available but no longer exists in the current setup\n","thinkingSignature":"2ba07a432c21bf7c2a2f426cb6062ed2ea90bef35ca3b64fb56ee18f64515902"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了。你说的是 **`openclaw-lark` 插件**（不是 CLI），里面有这些 Skill：\n\n- `feishu-create-doc` ✅ 曾经能创建飞书云文档\n- `feishu-bitable` ✅ 飞书多维表格\n- `feishu-calendar` ✅ 飞书日历\n- 等等……\n\n这是 2026年3月用过的东西，来源是 `openclaw-lark` 插件包。\n\n**但现在这个插件的 skill 目录里只剩 `tts-product-selection`**，其他 Skill 都没了（可能是后来更新被覆盖了，或者 skill 没装上）。\n\n你之前那个能创建飞书文档的 Agent 用的是 `openclaw-lark` 里的 `feishu-create-doc`。\n\n现在我给你装的是 clawhub 上的 `create-feishu-doc`，本质上是一样的功能。但需要对应的飞书应用（`agent-orchestrator`）有文档写权限且已发布。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4005,"output":448,"cacheRead":74496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78949,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopRea