{"type":"message","id":"74ae8072","parentId":"09a3e92a","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:11:08.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! There's a global npm package `@larksuite/cli` installed. But looking at the `openclaw-lark` extension, it only has a `skills` directory with `tts-product-selection` in it. It seems like `openclaw-lark` is a community plugin that came with some skills pre-bundled, but not the `feishu-create-doc` that the user is remembering.\n\nThe user is saying: \"我是用他官方提供的这个文件发给智能体，直接就可以安装了\" - meaning they previously shared a file with an AI agent, and the agent was able to directly install/use it.\n\nThe `@larksuite/cli` is the official Feishu CLI tool, version 1.0.23. \n\nSo the official Feishu CLI is installed globally as `@larksuite/cli` v1.0.23, which means the user likely shared this with an agent before. When they send the Feishu bot a message, the Feishu channel delivers it to OpenClaw, which then routes it to the appropriate agent based on the bindings in openclaw.json.\n","thinkingSignature":"e0570fb1a654d2689d8f728a2a2f12c625dadc31828c9f3bda9c0d4c5b29874d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n找到了！\n\n**`@larksuite/cli@1.0.23`** 已全局安装，路径是 `/home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/@larksuite/cli/bin/lark-cli`。\n\n但 `openclaw-lark` 插件目录里只剩 `skills/tts-product-selection`，`feishu-create-doc` 等 Skill 不知何时被移除了。\n\n**你说的\"官方文件发给智能体直接安装\"** —— 飞书官方 CLI 包里有 Skill 吗？还是有其他单独的安装包？\n\n我看看 `@larksuite/cli` 里有没有预置 Skill：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lqk3n00z97xh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/@larksuite/cli -name \"SKILL.md\" -o -name \"*.skill.md\" 2>/dev/null; ls /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/@larksuite/cli/scripts/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":436,"output":441,"cacheRead":80000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80877,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheR