{"type":"message","id":"f59640d0","parentId":"1cfeec23","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:14:11.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The npm install failed because the directory already exists. The `@larksuite/cli` is already installed. Let me check if it's already there and proceed with Step 2 - asking the user how they want the AI to work with them.\n","thinkingSignature":"f3315e675d064ab950224f640e3714890b37feea6f043c54b4adff12c8049348"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n`@larksuite/cli` 已经装好了，直接跳到 Step 2。\n\n**Agent 编排工程师** 需要你确认它的工作方式：\n\n- **As bot** — 以机器人身份工作，用自己的飞书应用身份。适合群聊、团队通知、共享文档。**（推荐这个）**\n- **As user** — 以你的身份工作，能访问你的个人飞书数据。**⚠️ 如果选这个：不要把这个机器人分享给他人或加入群聊——它有权限访问你的个人数据。**\n\n选哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":318,"output":162,"cacheRead":85760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86240,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778411645056,"responseId":"064f9b7d56e7249c5f9e1f34be76593e"}}
